findings.title: Authorized account can change the maximum transaction amount.
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to modify the maximum allowed transaction amount.

findings.title: Authorized account can include in and exclude from dividends.
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to include or exclude addresses from receiving dividends.

findings.title: Authorized Account Can Include/Exclude Fee and Transaction Amount
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to include or exclude fees and transaction amounts, which can lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Authorized account can change fees.
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to modify fee settings, which could lead to potential security risks and unintended consequences.

findings.title: Authorized account can change fee receivers.
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to modify the fee receivers, which could lead to unauthorized changes and potential security risks.

findings.title: Authorized account can change swap threshold and disable/enable swap
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to modify the swap threshold and enable or disable the swap functionality.

findings.title: Authorized account can change target liquidity values
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to modify target liquidity values, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Authorized account can change distribution criteria.
findings.description: The authorized account has the capability to modify the distribution criteria, which may lead to unintended consequences and potential security risks.

findings.title: Authorized account can change distribution GAS
findings.description: The authorized account has the capability to alter the distribution of GAS, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner Can Withdraw BNBs to Marketing Receiver Address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw BNBs to the marketing receiver address without any restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can change trading status.
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the trading status, which could lead to potential security risks if not properly managed.

findings.title: Owner can change cooldown status.
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the cooldown status, which may lead to unintended consequences or security risks.

findings.title: Authorized account can change buybackKeepItSimple value
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to modify the buybackKeepItSimple value, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Authorized account can change addresses' isTimelockExempt value
findings.description: The authorized account has the privilege to modify the isTimelockExempt value of addresses.

findings.title: Owner can change max wallet amount restriction.
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum transaction amount, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit.
findings.description: The contract may be vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to the block gas limit.
